{"tid":966548,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水務署擬2022年北區供應再造水沖廁","createTime":"2019-01-03T01:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T20:35:04.000Z","uid":23707,"like":96,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"0791a2c55c30aa324dba613bae5eb92a3efcc405","tid":966548,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:32:48.000Z","msg":"水務署署長黃仲良在一個電台節目表示，經過公眾諮詢，公眾大部分支持發展循環再用水，署方會因應石湖墟污水處理廠提升處理能力，率先將區內污水加工處理生產再造水，由2022年起，逐步向新界東北地區供應再造水取代食水沖廁。<br />\n<br />\n黃仲良指出，屆時上水粉嶺等地用水沖廁，不再需要收水費，大部分樓宇亦毋須重新接駁喉管，而再造水亦會染色，以免市民誤用作其他用途。<br />\n<br />\n至於安達臣等新發展區，他表示，水務署正在發展重用浴室及廚房用水作沖廁等非飲用用途，相信區內的生活污水已經可以支持沖廁所需。他估計，全面落實後，每年可以節省2100萬立方米食水，佔全港每年用水量約2%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d166174bcc7ea3a74f26364feb56255250a4d1","tid":966548,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:34:36.000Z","msg":"點解唔用鹹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f54e1e7d7756498720c236916c490b7cc925a0","tid":966548,"uid":40839,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"51d166174bcc7ea3a74f26364feb56255250a4d1","tid":966548,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:34:36.000Z","msg":"點解唔用鹹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"用咸水年年爆幾次屎渠<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ae0ca86352bc1f7e870c986915737d54065d66","tid":966548,"uid":57677,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"97f54e1e7d7756498720c236916c490b7cc925a0","tid":966548,"uid":40839,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"51d166174bcc7ea3a74f26364feb56255250a4d1","tid":966548,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:34:36.000Z","msg":"點解唔用鹹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:50:50.000Z","msg